Initially, heat the oil, add few cubes of butter based on the quantity of the paneer taken
Add some spices like cumin seeds, cinamom etc
Add onion, Mirchi and curry leave
Also add some giner garlic paste 
After a while add chopped tamatoes and let it cook
Before cooking this dish, chop paneer into small pieces and smash a little for taste
Fry it in oil where the water is absorbed and paneer boils, roasts
In the initial pan, after adding ginger garlic paste add the fried panner(smashed paneer also)
Let the entire dish cook for some more time 
If needed add additional spices like masala powder
